###  urn:webprotege:ontology:c73d2ce1-09f8-451b-b6fd-d3ba1ee14c49#endZone
:endZone rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
         rdfs:domain <http://webprotege.stanford.edu/R8gcQaW839Or2hVYprhpSK8> ;
         rdfs:range <http://webprotege.stanford.edu/R7cZlQsX1sMesyLmlHKw2lg> .



